{
  "stem": "19211.1",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 290.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But they were getting all the Jews from the ghettos-- 1942 or so, as far as I can remember.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they said they're going to evacuate us, take us all.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We didn't-- they didn't know where.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But all the Jews are going to have to leave.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They're going to take us, whole lot, which was, of course, I know now they went to Auschwitz and other camps.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we were preparing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was about four or five Jewish families in that village, Ponikwa.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were building a bunker there in the woods.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were familiar with the territory there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we were building with them a bunker for a few families.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we-- when things got really bad, when they, they, they'd-- all the Jews from the villages had to move to the town, to the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We didn't want to go to the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we went to the woods, in hiding.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they-- and then the whole story begins.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Then it got rough again, completely rough.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We were--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because we heard that they were taking all the Jews away.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We didn't know where.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We didn't want to go.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We didn't know where they were going.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They said they were evacuating.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We were just-- had a premonition that it wasn't good.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Feeling it wasn't good, you know, something wasn't right.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So-- and I guess there were some witnesses that came back from the camps and told what the-- which people didn't believe what was happening.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I didn't know much about it at that time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We didn't have any-- no news like you have here, no newspapers, nothing.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We didn't know what was happening.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We just knew that things were getting bad.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A lot of killings.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
